name: JTWeatherProject
tagline: 5 day forecast demo app using the OpenWeather API
body:
### Welcome JTWeatherProject.
This app uses the OpenWeatherAPI to get forecasts for the next 5 days. See podfile for full list of dependencies. 

### Design
Flat 5 day TableView with Blur overlay

### Author
